[src:thiserror-rust/type-system] As this example shows, C is not memory-safe.
[src:thiserror-rust/type-system] As arbitrary data was assumed to be a character, it is also not a type-safe language.
[src:thiserror-rust/type-system] In general, type-safety and memory-safety go hand in hand.
